## IV. A/B TESTING PROTOCOL (handoff)

### Pick 2, không phải 3

A/B test cùng lúc 3 variant = chia traffic 3 chiều = mất statistical significance.

**Recommended order**:
1. **Round 1**: A (Frustration) vs B (Readiness) — biggest hypothesis test
2. **Round 2** (sau winner): Winner vs C — refinement test

### Sample size & duration

- **Minimum 200 click/variant** trước khi conclude
- **Run tối thiểu 7 ngày** để cover day-of-week variation
- **Statistical significance**: aim for ≥10% diff với ≥200 sample/variant

### Metrics to track

| Metric | Where measure |
|--------|---------------|
| **CTR ad → page** | FB Ads Manager / GA |
| **Scroll depth** | Hotjar / GA scroll tracking |
| **Time on page** | GA |
| **Form submit / Click CTA** | GA event |
| **Conversion rate (sale)** | Payment gateway / GA conversion |

### Common A/B test mistakes (avoid)

❌ Test nhiều variable cùng lúc (headline + CTA + price) — không biết cái nào win
❌ Stop sớm (3 ngày 50 clicks) — noise, không signal
❌ Pick variant subjective ("em thấy A đẹp hơn") — test data, không gut
❌ Forget significance — diff 1-2% trong 100 sample = noise

